Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:07.01,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:10.39,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In this kingdom where magic is everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.39,0:00:12.95,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,there is one boy who can't use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.35,0:00:15.61,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:18.95,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,With guts and hard work, \Nhe made it into the Magic Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:21.84,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and he never gave up, \Ndespite how much he got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.84,0:00:24.65,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He continues to diligently aim for the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:27.79,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you are a peasant,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:29.63,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,or even if you're poor...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:32.38,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone in this world can still shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:34.80,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He's working hard to prove that,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.23,0:00:37.85,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and to become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:48.23,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and some of the other Black Bulls\N were gathered up by Mereoleona,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:52.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and taken away to train along \Nwith the Crimson Lion Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:55.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get to the goal first!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:57.32,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,No, it'll be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:57.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:01:01.62,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Magic: Spiral Flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:07.04,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,During their training, a new \Ndungeon appeared before them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.17,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Things are getting exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:13.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.50,0:01:16.84,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Leopold, who sees himself as Asta's rival,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:20.68,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,showed great growth as they \Nconquered the dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:24.48,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,I will learn how to fully use that \Nspell and become stronger than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:27.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll become \Neven stronger than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:30.00,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And thus, their training ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:31.53,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Or so they thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:35.21,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.21,0:01:37.65,italics,All,0000,0000,0000,,She's actually here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.27,0:01:40.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:42.86,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Take care, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:47.36,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,You've been chosen to deal with an \Nurgent matter of grave importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.36,0:01:49.50,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,You should be honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:14.86,Ep Title,Ep,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(210,1871)\t(210,2419,\fscx120\fscy120)}Those Who Have Been Gathered
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:27.72,sign_5790_50_Mereoleona_Vermi,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Vermillion Residence
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:33.85,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,You two, hurry up and take a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:35.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:40.57,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,The Vermillion residence. \NIn other words, my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:45.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Mimosa, Mimosa's bro,\N and Captain Fuegoleon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:47.91,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I see that you've been summoned as well, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:51.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, more like we were dragged here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:55.94,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Asta. You're as unsightly as ever,\N and now, a wanted fugitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:04:01.47,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess I must admit that your recent deeds \Nmay have been at least a {\i1}little{\i0} beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:07.05,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that was my brother's \Nattempt to compliment you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:10.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So... why are we all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:12.81,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.90,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Fuegoleon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:21.53,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I may be guessing, but this seems quite serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:23.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:27.88,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we're receiving special orders \Nregarding the Spade Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:28.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:30.12,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:36.54,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,We are about to hold a very important meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:40.06,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:45.18,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,that the results of this meeting will \Naffect the very future of our kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:49.18,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You must make sure you tell no one of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:51.60,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This must be a top-secret mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.10,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let us begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:06.20,sign_5790_50_Mereoleona_Vermi,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(760,1)}Theresa Rapual
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:05.65,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The old sister lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:09.19,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Um... May I ask who she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:11.76,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,She's one of the sisters \Nfrom the church in Nean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:13.95,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But why is she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:20.79,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,This meeting is to celebrate Ms. Theresa's \Nfifteen years in the sisterhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:22.16,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:27.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But wait, you guys just said this will \Naffect the very future of our kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:31.64,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Theresa is currently raising \Nchildren, who have a future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:35.52,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,So, as I said, this affects the \Nvery future of our kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:38.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess that's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:41.82,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Why must we not mention this to anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:44.47,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,We're not saying to keep this a complete secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:47.74,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,We just mean that there's really \Nno reason to tell others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:51.94,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Theresa dislikes flashiness and \Nthings that bring attention to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:55.00,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't a secret mission at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:58.87,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,This is already too flashy and grandiose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:01.50,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I just want some peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:04.97,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, we're just \Nhaving a party to celebrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:07.63,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you decide to host this, Fuegoleon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:12.91,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,When I was young, Ms. Theresa was in \Ncharge of my sister's and my education
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:16.39,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,while doing her duties as a Magic Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:20.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I guess you did mention \Nthat before, Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:24.82,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief. If nothing else, \Nyour heads sure have gotten bigger,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:27.26,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Mereo and Fueggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:28.62,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Mereo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:30.07,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Fueggy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.06,0:06:35.18,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,After retiring from being our \Ntutor and a Magic Knight,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:39.74,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,today marks fifteen years \Nsince you became a sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:41.61,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I also heard that you acted
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:45.97,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,valiantly during the kidnapping \Nincident that occurred in Nean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:49.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Granny was super amazing back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:57.39,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,We will celebrate her greatness and \Nhonor her lifelong achievements today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:00.81,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,We called you lot here to help celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:03.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I finally figured it all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:06.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, we need to make \Nthis a huge celebration!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:07.74,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:08.65,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:10.24,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,How beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:11.62,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking about your looks,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:14.66,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,but there is beauty residing \Nin your proud spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:18.62,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finally beginning to \Nunderstand that kind of beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:22.44,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,But of course, I'm still the most beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:26.80,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,It may be too late, but would you \Nconsider educating my brother, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:29.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why isn't Leo here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:33.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is a party to celebrate someone \Nreally important to his siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:36.58,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Under ordinary circumstances, \Nwe would have summoned him here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:41.57,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,but he requested that he be allowed \Nfurther training, which I granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:43.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:46.48,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,That boy's got a good head on his shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:50.20,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,You two don't have time to waste \Non nonsense like this either, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:53.22,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,This celebration is just \Nfor today. Please enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:08:00.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! This all looks super good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:02.25,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Theresa, please enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:07.10,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,It could be because I've been away \Nfrom the royal capital for so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:11.09,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,but I really don't care for fancy meals like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:14.14,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,This is exactly why I thought about declining.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:14.97,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:16.85,main,Girl B,0000,0000,0000,,It's a feast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:17.68,main,Boy B,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:19.35,main,Girl B,0000,0000,0000,,It looks so yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:24.44,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,You offered to feed my \Nlittle ones, so I couldn't say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:26.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Marie! And the other kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:29.46,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Asta! Thank you for helping us before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:31.07,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.24,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:33.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:35.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This ki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:37.71,main,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,Asta! Come on, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:39.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:42.26,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, line up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:43.88,main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:47.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go. This is yours, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:48.84,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:50.80,main,Kid Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Tch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:52.81,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:56.09,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,You may have fooled the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:09:00.77,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,but did you really think \Nyou could fool me, Gauche?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:02.52,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it, you old hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:07.40,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm guessing you had some transformation \Nwizard help you transform into a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:11.65,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure I remember your \Nsquad having someone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:14.88,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the church because \NI wanted to see Marie,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:17.24,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,but then I heard there was \Na party being held here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.46,0:09:21.58,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm here. You got a \Nproblem with that, you shitty old hag?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:24.30,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're as foul-mouthed as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:28.03,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,You're fully aware that you're only \Nallowed to see Marie once a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:31.59,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,How desperate are you to see her, \Nyou sister-obsessed punk?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:36.59,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't count as my one time a month if \NI'm just sneaking a peek, you wicked old hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:40.78,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to interrupt the fun, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:43.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?! The party's already over?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:45.57,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.57,0:09:47.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:52.44,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I need you all to do a party trick \Nthat will delight Ms. Theresa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:53.92,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:04.12,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Now, show us your party tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:08.79,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,He wants us to do... party tricks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:11.26,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He wants {\i0}me{\i1} to do a party trick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:14.44,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What do tricks have to do with parties?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:17.35,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Fueggy's always been \Na bit on the awkward side,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.35,0:10:19.72,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,so he doesn't know how else to phrase things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:24.57,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'd like to ask all of you \Nto entertain the children, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:27.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So we just gotta entertain everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:28.87,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:36.22,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to me. My beauty always \Nquenches the masses' thirst for entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:40.51,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,In your case, my dear brother, your whole \Nexistence is like a party trick,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:43.08,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,so you don't have to change a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:45.81,top,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,You flatter me, my dear sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:45.81,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Really? A party trick out of nowhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:47.37,top,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:52.71,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,At times like this, you mother, Lady Acier,\N would've been the first to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:57.37,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,At any banquet, she would entertain \Nus all with a brilliant party trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:00.47,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:03.41,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very excited to see \Nyour party trick, Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:05.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You've got this, Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:09.06,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you how royalty does a party trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:11.09,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:14.45,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,S-Something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:17.96,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that should do the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:18.92,main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:20.36,main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Do more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:22.20,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I shall go next.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:26.83,main,Kid gauche,0000,0000,0000,,They're so lame. I could \Nentertain Marie so much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:28.35,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,You shut your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:32.99,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Though, if you ask me, the fact that \Nyou've disguised yourself as a child
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:35.22,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,is probably the most hilarious thing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:37.25,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You never shut up, do you, old hag?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:39.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's what a party trick is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:40.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I've got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:43.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle! Throw me two plates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:44.38,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:48.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:50.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:52.85,main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:54.98,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Brilliant, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:57.81,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He's getting the biggest reaction.\N Not bad, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:03.41,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,What a bizarre party trick. I almost \Nfeel beauty in how unsightly it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:04.28,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, guys! Here comes the next one! Up they go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:08.53,main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:11.37,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, all of you. I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:10.84,top,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,You're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:14.86,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,So, what party trick are you \Ngoing to do for me, Fueggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:22.38,italics,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that I cannot get \Naway with doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:26.04,italics,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll have to use the ace up my sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:27.33,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:30.88,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,See these eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:39.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is Captain Fuegoleon doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:42.44,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Does he actually think he's boiling them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:45.41,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:51.69,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:55.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A hard-boiled egg, a soft-boiled egg,\N and a jammy soft-boiled egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:59.57,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,By carefully controlling my mana,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:02.21,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I can prepare eggs in three \Ndifferent ways at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:06.34,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,The jammy soft-boiled egg is \Nthe most difficult to execute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:10.31,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,To give the yolk a soft firmness while \Nkeeping the white in a gelatinous state,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:13.36,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,one must control the heat in the exact—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:14.31,main,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,Boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.31,italics,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:18.87,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,You're far too serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:21.25,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,You have no talent for this sort of thing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:22.32,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:25.32,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch. I'll show you how it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:28.48,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,One must have the right enthusiasm \Nwhen pulling off a party trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:36.71,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,This is how it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:39.58,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Are you not entertained?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:42.40,main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.38,main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,That lady's mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:46.39,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Why in the world are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:49.14,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I see you two are as clueless as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:52.52,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for this shameful display.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:54.47,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,But I can see that you haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:58.65,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing has changed at all \Nsince I looked after you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:02.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What were they like back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:03.53,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:08.78,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they were very capable, but still \Na handful. That's how I'd describe them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:14.35,flashback,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be your tutor starting today.\N I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:17.79,flashback,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Theresa! I must become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:20.33,flashback,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,So please, train me harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:22.70,flashback,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous, Fueggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:25.46,flashback,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,No one can become strong overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:28.28,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Fueggy seemed unsatisfied with my training
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:30.57,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,and would always sneak around,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:32.97,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,training more on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:37.50,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Training too much when you're too young \Naffects your mana and your growth,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:39.78,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,so I struggled to get him to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:43.46,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,As for Mereo, she was always a wild child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:45.48,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,She never listened to me \Nanyway, so I let her be,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:47.52,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,and she became overpowered on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:52.55,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I was their tutor for about ten years,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:57.07,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,until Fueggy was fifteen \Nand Mereo was seventeen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:15:00.37,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I do apologize for being such an\Nunruly student, Ms. Theresa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:03.51,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Because you let me have my freedom back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:06.35,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to become strong without \Nbeing stuck in constraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:08.13,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very grateful to you, Ms. Theresa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:11.38,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I just did my job as your tutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:13.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Granny,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:16.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess they've been amazing \Never since they were kids, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.42,0:15:17.99,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:21.04,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Fueggy couldn't control his mana,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:24.15,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,so he'd always set things on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.23,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:30.73,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,I remember that. And every time you \Nstarted a fire, you'd cry like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:35.37,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,And when you were about eight, Mereo,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:38.37,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,you got too worked up and set \Nyour own clothes on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.61,0:15:42.12,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I do believe I recall that happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.41,0:15:44.50,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I do remember that, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:48.07,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,When you're born with overwhelming mana,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:50.38,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,that's bound to happen when \Nyou're still children.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:56.69,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,But as you grow, eventually, \Nyou naturally become able to control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:16:01.73,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So compared to others,\N I was just a late bloomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:05.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So it's like getting \Nover wetting the bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:09.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're older than ten, it mostly \Ncalms down, but there are those kids
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:11.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,who still wet the bed at, \Nlike, thirteen or fourteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:14.85,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, exactly. It's similar to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:17.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! So just like wetting the bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:19.78,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you, Stupidsta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:20.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:21.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck did I just get slapped?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:28.80,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, all kids have a couple of \Nembarrassing memories like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:33.88,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of embarrassing memories, \NI happen to remember Fuegoleon
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:37.05,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,breaking a vase that was a \Nprecious family heirloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:40.93,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,I actually took the blame for it \Nso he wouldn't get in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.56,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I beg your pardon, dear sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:47.06,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,but it was you who actually broke \Nthe vase and blamed it on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:50.21,main,Fuegoloen,0000,0000,0000,,I know it happened a long time ago, \Nbut I cannot allow you to forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:54.18,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Oho, so that's how you think you remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:56.45,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,It's not how I remember it. \NIt is the simple truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:17:01.88,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,When you took Father's precious magic \Nitem without permission and lost it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:04.58,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,you also blamed that on me, didn't you, Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:09.46,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of your rubbish. Have you \Nforgotten that I'd let you off the hook
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:15.13,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,every single time you took a \Nportion from my dinner plate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.09,main,Fuegleon,0000,0000,0000,,That is also wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:19.06,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You were actually constantly \Ntaking a portion from
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:21.73,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,my dinner plate without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:27.21,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You may be my sister, but I will not \Nallow for any more of these falsities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:31.24,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Falsities? Watch your mouth, Fuegoleon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:33.61,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I would also like you to take back what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:38.49,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I'm going to have to \Nphysically teach you a lesson again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:40.83,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to see you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:45.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:49.25,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,What's new about siblings fighting?\N Just let them have at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:51.79,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Though... You there, missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.79,0:17:53.17,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:57.68,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want these kids to get hurt,\Nso could you protect them with your magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.94,0:17:59.80,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A-All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:05.06,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good, long look, kids. \NDon't end up like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:06.11,main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.11,0:18:10.65,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,It's not uncommon for kids to \Nremember things differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:13.93,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, protected Mimosa quite \Noften when we were children,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.93,0:18:16.50,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,but it appears as though my \Ndear sister has forgotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:19.45,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,What? When did you ever protect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:23.51,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,For example, the time I beautified \Na room after Mimosa sullied it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:25.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.65,0:18:27.08,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I must ask you to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:29.90,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Especially in front of Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:33.67,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, every time you \Nclaimed to be practicing magic
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:37.76,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,while littering flower petals all over the \Nhouse, it was I who cleaned them all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:40.51,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I do believe that's just a matter of opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:43.93,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please stop playing dumb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.74,0:18:47.50,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I am beautiful, and therefore, \NI do not like conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:50.44,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,However, I shall not allow \Nyou to slander my good name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:54.45,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I am tired of your excuses, Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:57.82,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,so I shall gladly shut your mouth for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:19:02.45,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure I've ever seen Mimosa like this.\N I guess strange things do happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:04.95,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.53,0:19:09.53,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Looks like you'll at least \Nbe able to entertain me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:16.59,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you jackasses! \NYou're putting Marie in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:21.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Gauche?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:22.59,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:25.92,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let any of you get \Na chance to hurt Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.87,0:19:33.56,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business! I'm in the middle \Nof disciplining my idiot of a brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:39.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting way out of hand, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:53.25,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:00.59,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:04.18,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,She completely stopped all \Nthe fights in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:05.76,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:13.94,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, all siblings fight, \Nbut there are limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.18,0:20:18.11,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry that I lost my \Ncomposure with you, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:20.94,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Nay, I just failed to be beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:25.20,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,As for you two, it seems like \Nyou need a stern talking-to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:43.74,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,You're both over thirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:46.01,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fighting hard enough to \Nbring your own house down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.23,0:20:48.39,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We're terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:52.29,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hang on a damn second, you old hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.97,0:20:55.69,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell do you look so smug?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.03,0:20:58.86,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I was wondering where you went.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:00.52,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,You only got in trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:03.36,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,because you came here when you're \Nnot supposed to, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:04.53,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:09.40,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad your sister is so much \Nmore intelligent than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:11.87,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:14.62,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for looking out for the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.31,0:21:16.62,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,N-No problem, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:19.35,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's about time we headed home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:21.46,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Theresa! Are you heading home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:23.88,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of you two for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.39,0:21:27.50,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize again for our rudeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.50,0:21:31.17,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,So please, allow us to do \Nsomething nice for you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:34.94,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,This only happened because you tried to \Ndo something you're not accustomed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:37.17,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that we're inexperienced, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:42.95,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll gladly accept your feelings, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:44.74,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,How about...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:50.50,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,you celebrate my hundred years \Nof continued service in about 85 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:55.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The Crimson She-Leopard is so damn cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:58.53,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure she could \Ntake down a devil on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:02.24,main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,That was so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.53,0:22:07.52,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't lived all these years as an \Nold hag with nothing to show for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:41.31,main,noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Another mixer?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:43.77,main,noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is Finral thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.77,0:23:48.86,main,Some,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 135: \N"The One Who Has My Heart, My Mind, and Soul."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.61,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 135\N\N{\fs18}The One Who Has My Heart, My Mind, and Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:53.76,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, Stupidsta. The one who \Nhas my heart? I-I'm royalty!
